name: Mainline Greenway Bike Delaware County
description: The Mainline Greenway/Bike Delaware County is project-based on Lancaster Ave, Haverford. This project aims to create a bike line for all of the residents that use their bicycle as their primary mode of transportation, the Mainline Greenway. The general goal of the project is to get Haverford's residents involved in the infrastructure of their own town. It aims to re-imagine the street infrastructure of Haverford Township as well as the Delaware and Montgomery County to accommodate healthier ways of transportation.
